          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?q=80&w=400&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Teacher" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500" loading="lazy">
